{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "MPE Demo Preparation",
  "description": "Pre-demo checklist. Builds the SharePoint standalone HTML package, runs the MX 2026-04-22 manual simulation checklist in rehearsal mode, validates all 10 markets + regions are current, and generates the 90-second demo script. Run ~30 minutes before any leadership demo.",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "1. Run the data audit and confirm no market has regressed since the last refit: `python3 -m shared.tools.prediction.data_audit`. If any market shows a fallback recommendation change, flag it \u2014 the demo story may need adjustment.\n2. Run the core acceptance test (equivalent of running `kiro hook run mpe-acceptance-core`). Report pass/fail for each of the 10 markets + 3 regions.\n3. Build the SharePoint standalone HTML: `python3 shared/dashboards/export-projection-data.py --standalone`. Push to Kiro-Drive/Artifacts/strategy/projection-engine.html via sharepoint_write_file. Confirm it renders by reading back the file header.\n4. Walk through the MX 2026-04-22 manual simulation checklist (shared/wiki/agent-created/operations/mpe-mx-422-simulation.md). For each of the 10 steps, state the expected output and confirm the current engine produces it. Flag any step whose expected output has drifted \u2014 this is a signal that recent parameter updates changed the MX narrative.\n5. Read shared/wiki/agent-created/operations/mpe-demo-script.md (the 90-second script). Update the numbers in the script to match the latest MX Q2 projection at 75% ie%CCP. Tell Richard: 'Here are the three numbers to memorize: total regs {X}, spend ${Y}M, 70% CI [{L}, {H}].'\n6. Tell Richard what environment to demo from: if Kiro dashboard is live use that; else use the SharePoint standalone. Confirm the URL is reachable.\n7. End with a readiness summary: 'DEMO READY: all 10 markets + 3 regions acceptance-green, SharePoint standalone at {URL}, MX 4/22 checklist rehearsed, demo script memorized.' OR surface exactly what's blocking readiness.\nRichard has a leadership demo coming up. Run the full pre-demo checklist and report readiness.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"
  }
}